Happy Valley area 2 bedroom 2 Bath San Rafael home. Walking distance to San Rafael High, Whole Foods, Montecito shopping center and downtown. Hardwood floors in open areas, carpet in bedrooms, washer &amp; dryer included, laundry room w/sink, dishwasher, refrigerator, oven and gas cooktop. Covered back patio and standalone storage shed. Gardener service provided by landlord. All utilities by tenant. Pets negotiable, no smoking, credit check and renters insurance. Available August 1st and 1 year lease desired $3,150/mo + security deposit. Thanks<br>
